plot: Ohhhh, Mama! Johnny Bravo is a blond egomaniac who just loves pretty women. With spoofs of Schoolhouse Rock, The Twilight Zone, and other television shows and movies, Johnny Bravo, along with his mother Bunny and his cute neighbor Suzy, Johnny learns more about life - the hard way.   Written by  Ian Pugh
